---
title: Cheesy BBQ Beef and Rice Bowls with Crispy Shallots
description: These hearty BBQ-spiced beef bowls feature a flavourful mix of peppers and onions served over a bed of fluffy rice. Each bowl is topped with a drizzle of tangy BBQ sauce and crispy shallots for added crunch.

